<title>ạ̉nạ jạylk rby ḥbyby yswʿ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- ạ̉nạ jạylk rby ḥbyby yswʿ msẖtạq frḥạn
 msẖtạq llʿsẖrẗ mʿạk yạ yswʿ ạ̉nạ byk hymạn
 ạ̹rwyny bḥbk rby yswʿ qlby ʿṭsẖạn ạ̉gẖmrny bḥbk rby yswʿ ạ̉nạ msẖ sẖbʿạn
 1- (ạ̉nạ jạylk ạqwlk rby yswʿ ạ̉nạ lyk wạnạ mlkk
 wdh ʿhd ạlḥb ạlạ̉bdy ạlly ạnt mḍyth bdmk)2
 ạ̉gẖmrny bḥbk rby yswʿ ạ̉nạ msẖ sẖbʿạn
 2- (ḥbk byṭmn nfsy yạrby wysẖjʿny
 byzyl ạlkẖwf wytẖbt qlby wbyrfʿny)2
 ạ̉gẖmrny bḥbk rby yswʿ ạ̉nạ msẖ sẖbʿạn
 3- (yạ yswʿ fy ḥnạnk qwẗ btsẖfy kl ạ̉mrạḍy
 wblmsẗ ạ̹ydk bạkẖd brkẗ tsd ḥạjạty)2
 ạ̉gẖmrny bḥbk rby yswʿ ạ̉nạ msẖ sẖbʿạn</lyrics>
